{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 27.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just, these were false shower heads, what we figured out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went and we found some English-speaking inmates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, things by now are beginning to be organized.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the military had enough sense to let the structure of the camp itself organize it, because they could never-- never could have done it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no way, without killing a bunch of people, could you have got that under control.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to let the inmates, the power structure, settle things down and take charge.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's exactly what they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you had a lot of muscle there, but you couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't use it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the inmates were basically running the show pretty much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We get ready to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had-- in the house that I was living, boy, I had a real nice house with a balcony.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, or my room was where I could go out there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and I had my own bathroom, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had-- I had my kit, my shaving kit and all that stuff.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I'll be damned if I could get rid of that-- and I had a change, a new un-- a clean uniform, my before bag.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I changed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I polished my shoes, because the shoes were all crappy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I changed into an Eisenhower jacket and left my flight jacket in there, because it stunk to beat hell.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I had that smell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I couldn't-- shampooed my hair with that brown G.I.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Soap, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And even tried to dissolve some in water so I could pour over me thinking, boy, this stuff is like lye, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I still-- I still smelled.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
